## 2. Architecture Overview — Cognitive Layer Stack

The system is organized into strictly isolated cognitive layers. **No layer may automatically contaminate another.** Data flows down the stack only through explicit, authorized transitions.

```
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  LAYER 0 — RAW INGEST                                           ║
║  raw_ingest_{uid}                                               ║
║  Provenance: OBSERVED                                           ║
║  First-person baseline truth. Drop zone → parse → embed → store ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  LAYER 1 — MEMORY                                               ║
║  memory_{uid}                                                   ║
║  Provenance: INFERRED                                           ║
║  Versioned semantic categories derived from raw ingest only.    ║
║  Longitudinal. Append-only. Never overwritten.                  ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  LAYER 2 — TRENDS                                               ║
║  entity_registry_{uid} (trend fields)                           ║
║  Provenance: CALCULATED                                         ║
║  Objective directional measurements. No confidence score.       ║
║  Mathematical, not probabilistic.                               ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  LAYER 3 — PREDICTIONS                                          ║
║  predictions_{uid}                                              ║
║  Provenance: PREDICTED                                          ║
║  Probabilistic hypotheses with confidence scores.               ║
║  Bayesian-weighted. Expire or resolve. Never permanent.         ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  LAYER 4 — HORIZON SCAN  [SANDBOXED]                           ║
║  horizon_scan_{uid}                                             ║
║  Provenance: RETRIEVED                                          ║
║  External world intelligence. Strictly quarantined.             ║
║  CANNOT write to layers 0-3 automatically. Ever.               ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  LAYER 5 — ALERTS                                               ║
║  alerts_{uid}                                                   ║
║  Provenance: RETRIEVED + CALCULATED                             ║
║  High-priority operational interruptions only.                  ║
║  Bypass queue. Strict criteria. Not a notification feed.        ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

SHARED (cross-user, no behavioral data):
  shared_entity_registry   canonical identity + aliases only
```

**Collections per user:** `raw_ingest_{uid}`, `memory_{uid}`, `entity_registry_{uid}`, `predictions_{uid}`, `horizon_scan_{uid}`, `alerts_{uid}`  
**Shared:** `shared_entity_registry`  
**No graph database.** Multi-hop traversal in application code. Revisit only if hops > 4 or dataset exceeds personal scale.  
**No separate compactor.** Memory agent is the single intelligence layer.

