## 15. What This System Does NOT Do

Explicit non-goals. Do not implement these.

- **No generative responses.** Returns structured data. Calling AI agent narrates.
- **No real-time streaming.** Background async processes. Query returns pre-computed memory.
- **No cross-user behavioral data.** Query for alice never touches bob. Ever.
- **No automatic deletion.** Append-only. Manual deletion via explicit admin API only.
- **No Neo4j.** Application-code traversal. Revisit only at > 4 hops or non-personal scale.
- **No automatic external→memory promotion.** Horizon scan items require explicit human action to internalize. A language model acting autonomously cannot trigger internalization.
- **No confidence scores on trends.** Trends are mathematical facts. Only predictions carry confidence scores.
- **No LLM in the trend calculation path.** Trends are computed with `numpy`/`scipy`. The LLM never touches the trend calculator.
- **No unbounded web crawling.** Scout only queries for entities already in the personal entity registry, restricted to the last N days. It is not a news aggregator.
- **No interruptions for non-critical events.** Bypass escalation is reserved for physical safety and infrastructure death criteria only. Political news, market movements, and general industry trends are never alerts.
